{"tid":2495614,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同唔同意男女拍拖頭幾個星期，女既就應該問男既下面有幾長？","createTime":"2021-04-19T09:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T12:58:14.000Z","uid":28068,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f649b4602f7e10fb31aa5dc58355c1e3aea12881","tid":2495614,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:37:30.000Z","msg":"見到好多女人對性能力好有要求<br />\n甚至放係選擇伴侶既首位<br />\n唔少人就算拍左幾年拖<br />\n最後都因為性生活唔夾 / 男既太短而分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得奇怪<br />\n你真係咁重視既<br />\n點解唔一齊左頭幾個星期就check清楚有幾長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解過左幾年發現唔夾你先至話人地廢<br />\n話人地浪費緊你青春？<br />\n人地都一樣有放時間同心機落你個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/coffin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有d女人又成日話愛係應該包容一切<br />\n唔好介意過去有幾多sp拍過幾多次拖<br />\n咁你又介意人短？<br />\n你根本就唔愛對方<br />\n對方值得更好既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n1. 女人鐘意推卸責任<br />\n2. 女人雙重標準，要求男人不論外表同過去真心愛自己，但原來自己咁睇重性能力"},{"pid":"2598063652fe1ee82020b355e1d6b0eb05c9985c","tid":2495614,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"青頭仔先會諗到嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7958e77e5c9c0f4d37fdf708ecf099197371b18","tid":2495614,"uid":343770,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"真係鍾意佢嘅話，應該可以包容到佢短嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff9244595375f97fd23bb57e15b98e762e5437c","tid":2495614,"uid":394002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2598063652fe1ee82020b355e1d6b0eb05c9985c","tid":2495614,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"青頭仔先會諗到嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:39:3